WEBVTT

00:06:29.865 --> 00:06:31.230
Namba sita

00:06:31.254 --> 00:06:34.758
(Vicheko)

00:06:34.782 --> 00:06:36.038
Kuandika.

00:06:36.874 --> 00:06:41.262
Kila mwandishi unayemjua huanaandika rasimu mbaya za mwanzo,

00:06:41.286 --> 00:06:43.439
Lakini hutuliza kitako kwenye kiti.

00:06:43.463 --> 00:06:45.183
Hiyo ndio siri ya maisha.

00:06:45.207 --> 00:06:48.407
Hiyo labda ndio tofauti kuu
kati yako na wao.

00:06:48.431 --> 00:06:49.893
Wanafanya tu.

00:06:49.917 --> 00:06:52.483
Wanafanya kwa makubaiano na wao wenyewe.

00:06:52.507 --> 00:06:54.550
Wanafanya katika deni la heshima yao.

00:06:55.336 --> 00:06:57.630
Wanasimulia hadithi kutokea kwao

00:06:57.654 --> 00:07:00.164
siku moja banda ya nyingine, kidogo kidogo.